parameters:
Poor quality oil has a strange smell, but this oil has no
odor. It was the same with the lamp at home.

Beastfolk with cat traits have good night vision, so they
don't need light, but having it is still nice. It's somehow
calming.

\n<Adventurer A>It's boring, isn't it? If we can get paid just for standing
around without anything happening, it's a good job, but it
makes me sleepy.

\n<Adventurer A>"It's not a full moon today, so we should be fine. Up until
now, everything has happened just as predicted. The main
event feels like it'll be in 4 or 5 days, huh?"

\n<Adventurer B>Tsk tsk tsk tsk! Baritstch! 0! Ah, I raised my own finger.
What a fool I am.

\n<Adventurer B>"Is it really okay to go with the same team? We let them
escape last time. Honestly, with that speed, it's
impossible."

It's a splendid gate. Made of fine wood. It would surely
feel great to sharpen my claws on it.
\n<Phantom Thief "L">As promised! I've done it once again♥
\n<Captain>Wait up~~~!!!
Damage2
Damage2
\n<Captain>Nnnngh! Nnnngh! Nnnngh!!!
\n<Phantom Thief "L">So long! Toodles~!
\n<Captain>Damn it! Blast it all!! Chase after them!!
\n<Adventurer A>So fast!! Which way did they go!?
\n<Adventurer B>Damn...! It's too dark...!
\n<Captain>Don't let them get away! Chase them! Chaaaase!!!

It's a splendid gate. I wonder where the phantom thief plans
to break in from. Could they have already sneaked in...?
That can't be the case, surely.

\n<Phantom Thief "L">I've graciously accepted the Howling Stone♥ Farewell,
everyone, and stay well-♪
\n<Captain>Stop right there!
Damage2
Damage2
\n<Captain>Nngh... Nngh... Nngh... Nngh... Nngh... Nngh...!!!
\n<Phantom Thief "L">Sorry for breaking my promise-!
\n<Captain>Grrr! How could I let this happen!! Chase after them!!

\n<Adventurer A>Too fast! What's with that movement? They're running on the
walls!
\n<Adventurer B>Haa... haa...! Where did they go!?
\n<Rui>...! This time for sure...!

The difference between this place and Dreamy can be told
just by the design of the door. Intricate designs are born
from abundance.

\n<Adventurer C>"Eh? You came from the lower guild? You're quite neat-
looking for someone from such a dirty place. Well, I won't
ask about your circumstances. I don't want to hear it
anyway."

\n<Adventurer C>"We are the adventurers of this town, the Rumare
Adventurer's Guild. Though I say that, we all come from
different places."

\n<Adventurer C>"The Noble Count seems different somehow. Before, he spoke
like a fool. But this time... it was as if he was a
different person."

\n<Adventurer C>"He had this distant look in his eyes, as if he was already
thinking about what happens after something's been stolen...
It might just be my imagination, though."

\n<Adventurer D>Ready, set, go! Right? What's with this "Barley Tits" thing.
Your hometown is crazy, huh.

\n<Adventurer D>"It was dark and hard to see, but last time, I thought I saw
someone who almost caught up with the phantom thief. Wasn't
that you?"
I tripped
What are you talking about?
こけた
\n<Rui>"I was so close, but then I tripped! Ehehe!"

\n<Rui>"I ended up falling over... If only there hadn't been a
stone there... Ahahaha."
\n<Adventurer D>"I see. Be careful where you step next time."
な、何のこと？

\n<Rui>"It was a total disaster! When I get surprised, I just
freeze up! You've got the wrong person!"

\n<Rui>"No! I don't think that was me! Yes! I got lost! I'm not
very familiar with this town..."
\n<Adventurer D>"Really? It looked like a silhouette with cat ears, though."

Through the window, I can see the empty cases. I bet they'll
be lined with delicious freshly baked bread in the morning.

It seems the tavern is temporarily closed today because
having too many people increases the security hassle. You
can tell the extent of the impact that the phantom thief
has.

There seems to be multiple people holding their breath in
the tavern with the lights out. It might not only be the
phantom thief who's after the Howling Stone.

\n<Rui>(It's quiet... Nothing's happening at all. Boring. Sigh.
Maybe I should just go home.)

\n<Rui>(It's quiet... It's so dull I might let my guard down. Maybe
I should wake myself up by talking to someone.)

\n<Rui>(Nnyaah... I'm getting sleepy... I need to talk to someone
to stay awake properly.)

\n<Rui>(Ugh... But it's so boring. It's impossible to stay on alert
all the time.)

\n<Former Sergeant>I've been demoted without a hitch due to my blunder. I'm a
former sergeant now. Such a pity...

\n<Rui>Cheer up! Is your leg okay? It made a snapping sound,
though.

\n<Former Sergeant>Hmm. However, the night breeze is cool today. This might not
be so bad after all.
\n<Rui>Is it true that you were buried under a tree?

\n<Former Sergeant>Hmm. Before, all I had to do was eat spaghetti through my
nose.
\n<Rui>(That sounds even tougher...)

\n<Former Sergeant>That's right, you were the fastest runner. I made sure the
handcuffs issued to you were the best ones. You're good at
playing chase, aren't you? I'm counting on you in case of an
emergency.

Favored by the upper class! Fluffy and chewy premium bread!
Perfect for a gift!
\n<Rui>I want to eat the pancakes that Jiiya baked...

\n<Rui>(Is it okay though? The premium bread boom seems to be
ending...)
\n<Lookout>Hey! Hey hey! Don't stray too far from your post!

\n<Lookout>All clear on this end! Make sure you guard the gate
properly!
